## 组件导出

### 页面/模块 components/index.ts

```js
export { default as MoveProduct } from './MoveProduct/index.vue'
export { default as FilterForm } from './FilterForm/index.vue'
```

### 页面内引用

```js
import { MoveProduct, FilterForm } from './components'
```

