## 路由定义

路由 `path` 由前端定义，**必须与页面目录对应**，必须添加 `webpackChunkName`：

| 路由 path | 页面位置 |
|-----------|----------|
| `/product/tag-list` | `views/product/tag-list/index.vue` |
| `/product/batch-off-shelf` | `views/product/batch-off-shelf/index.vue` |
| `/product/detail/:id` | `views/product/Detail.vue`（模块级单页例外） |

路由定义在**模块目录**下，主路由文件合并：

```ts
// views/product/routes.ts
export default [
  {
    path: '/product/tag-list',
    name: 'productTagList',
    component: () => import(/* webpackChunkName: "productTagList" */ './tag-list/index.vue'),
    meta: { title: '商品标签' },
  },
  {
    path: '/product/batch-off-shelf',
    name: 'productBatchOffShelf',
    component: () => import(/* webpackChunkName: "productBatchOffShelf" */ './batch-off-shelf/index.vue'),
    meta: { title: '批量下架' },
  },
  {
    path: '/product/detail',
    name: 'productDetail',
    component: () => import(/* webpackChunkName: "productDetail" */ './detail/index.vue'),
    meta: {
      title: '商品详情',
    }
  }
]
```

```ts
// router/index.ts
import productRoutes from '@/views/product/routes'

export const routes = [...productRoutes]
```

详见 `路由与权限规范.mdc`。

